sub_title: Data Analyst at Rabobank, New Horizons
summary:
I come with my work experience at United Nations and data science skills that I am mastering at Tilburg University. Feeling the power of data and how it can affect millions, I am motivated to use data at organizational level and for the best of society.

I am that colleague who works purposefully hard to see the result. Even though I prefer seeing products at the end of a working day, I never abstain from daily diplomacy and negotiations what contribute to sustainability of any work that I have undertaken .
